      "citation_id": "[CITATION_1]",
      "span_text": "In a study by Tory et al., it was shown that the R229Q variant only leads to a SRNS/FSGS phenotype when associated with certain NPHS2 mutations, specifically in exons 7 and 8 of the gene causing substitutions in C-terminal podocin"
